function removeOverride() {
// Remove styles that are overridign google animations on prioirty UI ready
// Google animations durring initial page load where bottle necking the CPU with force layouts and repaints.
let elem = document.querySelector("#google-load-override");
if (elem) {
elem.parentNode.removeChild(elem);
}
}
